Hey, this is Crash Adams Vault the ultimate place for all things Crash Adams!  Two best friends from Toronto who love creating pop/alternative music and sharing it with the world in the most unexpected ways. You‚Äôve probably seen them doing viral stunts in the middle of the street with their red couch, spreading smiles and music everywhere they go!

They write, produce, sing, mix, and master everything themselves and this channel is where you‚Äôll find exclusive moments, throwbacks, behind-the-scenes clips, and unreleased Crash Adams content you won‚Äôt see anywhere else.

If you love artists like Maroon 5, Harry Styles, Bruno Mars, Stellar, Imagine Dragons, Glass Animals, or Benson Boone, you‚Äôll feel right at home here. üí´
